            <title>[DERBY-3309] Minor cleanups in ClientPooledConnection40 and ClientPooledConnection</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3309</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A few minor cleanups:&lt;br/&gt;
 1) Remove unused constructor&lt;br/&gt;
 2) Remove unused imports&lt;br/&gt;
 3) Various documentation/formatting fixes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other minor fixes will be done if required.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
